metadata.name: Alpha Male Ape Club (AMAC)
metadata.description: Alpha Male Ape Club is an NFT collection of 10,000 unique apes on the Ethereum blockchain. These Alpha Male Apes from various walks of life have come together to show people that it's possible to love each other regardless of race, religion or views. They want to encourage us to make the world a better place where people live in peace and harmony.
